test.sql: SELECT "Calcs"."str0" AS "str0", SUM(CAST(TRUNC("Calcs"."int2") AS BIGINT)) AS "sum:int2:ok" FROM "Calcs" INNER JOIN ( SELECT COUNT(1) AS "_Tableau_join_flag", "Calcs"."str0" AS "str0", SUM(CAST(TRUNC("Calcs"."int2") AS BIGINT)) AS "$__alias__0" FROM "Calcs" GROUP BY 2 ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS LAST LIMIT 2 ) "t0" ON ("Calcs"."str0" = "t0"."str0") WHERE ((("Calcs"."str1" >= 'AIR PURIFIERS') AND ("Calcs"."str1" <= 'CD-R MEDIA')) OR (("Calcs"."str1" >= 'CONFERENCE PHONES') AND ("Calcs"."str1" <= 'ERICSSON'))) GROUP BY 1
